Don't push me away.

45
00:03:43,541 --> 00:03:44,541
I won't.

46
00:03:45,541 --> 00:03:48,166
You're not allowed to choose Xiang Bei.

47
00:03:50,708 --> 00:03:51,708
I only choose you.

48
00:03:57,500 --> 00:04:00,000
I like your minty scent.

49
00:04:03,208 --> 00:04:04,208
I know.

50
00:04:33,833 --> 00:04:34,833
Xu Yuan.

51
00:04:39,333 --> 00:04:40,333
Xu Yuan.

52
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:47,750
Xu Yuan.

53
