This is Xu Yuan's room.

54
00:05:56,875 --> 00:05:58,515
How did I end up back at Xu Yuan's place?

55
00:06:04,875 --> 00:06:05,875
Zhan Wang.

56
00:06:07,791 --> 00:06:08,791
Zhan Wang.

57
00:06:09,125 --> 00:06:10,125
I like you.

58
00:06:17,916 --> 00:06:18,916
You're awake.

59
