I made some hangover soup for you.

60
00:06:20,583 --> 00:06:21,583
Come out and have some.

61
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:34,500
Does your head hurt?

62
00:06:34,708 --> 00:06:36,748
That's what you get for
drinking so much yesterday.

63
00:06:36,916 --> 00:06:38,436
Hurry up and drink some hangover soup.

64
00:06:41,541 --> 00:06:43,041
Why am I at your place?

65
00:06:43,166 --> 00:06:43,958
Last night...

66
00:06:43,959 --> 00:06:45,166
You drank too much last night.

67
00:06:45,500 --> 00:06:46,500
Bian Ye found you,

68
00:06:46,666 --> 00:06:47,666
and then,

69
00:06:48,125 --> 00:06:49,351
I brought you back to my place.

70
00:06:49,375 --> 00:06:50,375
Did I...

71
00:06:50,666 --> 00:06:52,041
