72
00:06:54,791 --> 00:06:55,791
No.

73
00:06:56,083 --> 00:06:57,123
You were just a bit loud.

74
00:06:57,750 --> 00:06:58,750
Drink the soup.

75
00:07:00,166 --> 00:07:01,166
My head hurts.

76
00:07:01,291 --> 00:07:02,291
I really can't drink it.

77
00:07:12,291 --> 00:07:13,291
Just have some.

78
00:07:14,250 --> 00:07:15,250
It's good for you.

79
