82
00:07:41,375 --> 00:07:42,375
Um...

83
00:07:43,458 --> 00:07:44,875
Do you have any more mints?

84
00:07:46,250 --> 00:07:47,791
My mouth tastes weird.

85
00:07:47,916 --> 00:07:48,916
It's awful.

86
00:07:52,062 --> 00:07:52,968
Here.

87
00:08:17,375 --> 00:08:17,833
Look over there.

88
00:08:17,958 --> 00:08:19,118
