89
00:08:19,208 --> 00:08:20,791
A red-haired punk pretending to read.

90
00:08:21,125 --> 00:08:22,291
Exactly.

91
00:08:22,541 --> 00:08:23,166
I heard

92
00:08:23,333 --> 00:08:25,434
he's been running to the
suspended school doctor, Zhan,

93
00:08:25,458 --> 00:08:26,916
quite often lately.

94
00:08:27,125 --> 00:08:28,375
One is gay,

95
00:08:28,541 --> 00:08:29,541
the other is a punk.

96
00:08:29,583 --> 00:08:30,791
Asking for advice?

97
00:08:30,958 --> 00:08:31,958
Who are they kidding?

98
00:08:32,375 --> 00:08:34,059
It's obviously that kind
of disgusting relationship.

99
00:08:34,083 --> 00:08:35,583
Can you guys show some decency?

100
00:08:36,083 --> 00:08:37,791
How is him reading any of your business?

101
00:08:38,333 --> 00:08:39,583
What kind of person is Zhan Xu?

102
00:08:39,791 --> 00:08:41,031
What kind of person is Bian Ye?

103
00:08:41,208 --> 00:08:42,708
Who are you to judge them?

104
00:08:42,833 --> 00:08:43,875
I'll say whatever I want.

105
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,000
What's it to you?

106
00:08:45,375 --> 00:08:47,165
Don't tell me your jinx of a brother

107
00:08:47,166 --> 00:08:48,083
is also gay?

108
00:08:48,166 --> 00:08:49,166
You have a filthy mouth.

109
00:08:50,666 --> 00:08:52,906
Spending your time gossiping
about others' private lives

110
00:08:53,583 --> 00:08:55,125
doesn't make you any classier.

111
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,125
Everyone has

112
00:08:56,208 --> 00:08:57,833
the right to choose their own lifestyle.

113
00:08:58,083 --> 00:08:59,363
You don't have to understand it,

114
00:08:59,625 --> 00:09:00,945
but at least learn to respect it.

115
00:09:01,083 --> 00:09:02,708
Look who's playing the good guy now.

116
00:09:03,125 --> 00:09:04,208
Weren't you the one

117
00:09:04,416 --> 00:09:06,125
