118
00:09:06,375 --> 00:09:06,833
Yeah!

119
00:09:06,958 --> 00:09:07,416
Exactly!

120
00:09:07,416 --> 00:09:08,250
And now we're not allowed to talk?

121
00:09:08,333 --> 00:09:09,791
How ridiculous, shouting so loud.

122
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,000
Right?

123
00:09:11,916 --> 00:09:13,276
If you have a problem, come at me.

124
00:09:13,458 --> 00:09:14,458
Why yell at a girl?

125
00:09:15,041 --> 00:09:16,041
I'm right here.

126
00:09:16,333 --> 00:09:17,333
Say it to my face.

127
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:19,333
You're just a red-haired punk.

128
00:09:19,625 --> 00:09:21,142
We're saying you're
just like that damn queer.

129
00:09:21,166 --> 00:09:21,583
So what?

130
00:09:21,625 --> 00:09:22,625
Shut up!

131
00:09:22,708 --> 00:09:23,708
- You...
- Bian Ye.

132
00:09:29,458 --> 00:09:30,458
Zhan Xu.

133
00:09:31,041 --> 00:09:32,226
I... I didn't cause any trouble.

134
00:09:32,250 --> 00:09:33,250
I know.

135
00:09:38,250 --> 00:09:39,250
Why is he here?

136
00:09:41,250 --> 00:09:42,250
Lately,

137
00:09:43,041 --> 00:09:44,250
I know some of you

138
00:09:44,791 --> 00:09:45,833
are very interested in me.

139
00:09:46,500 --> 00:09:47,875
About my sexual orientation.

140
00:09:48,583 --> 00:09:49,833
I have already resigned,

141
00:09:51,333 --> 00:09:52,573
so it won't affect you anymore.

142
00:09:58,708 --> 00:09:59,708
Bian Ye...

143
00:10:00,333 --> 00:10:01,333
We are together now.

144
00:10:03,250 --> 00:10:04,500
I was the one who pursued him.

145
00:10:06,583 --> 00:10:08,875
I hope he can accept me.

146
00:10:08,958 --> 00:10:09,958
So it's true!

147
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:10,500
Really?

148
00:10:10,541 --> 00:10:11,541
I had no idea.

149
00:10:12,041 --> 00:10:13,458
So he was the one pursuing him.

150
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:14,375
What?

151
00:10:14,375 --> 00:10:15,375
This is really...

152
00:10:15,416 --> 00:10:16,767
Calling him a damn queer was spot on.

153
00:10:16,791 --> 00:10:17,791
Likewise,

154
00:10:18,166 --> 00:10:19,583
this is also between the two of us.

155
00:10:44,375 --> 00:10:45,416
Oh my god!

156
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:46,750
They're actually kissing!

157
00:11:14,500 --> 00:11:15,500
This...

158
00:11:16,958 --> 00:11:17,958
Oh my god!

159
00:11:23,250 --> 00:11:25,291
They're being so blatant!

160
00:11:25,375 --> 00:11:26,625
I can't believe it.

161
00:11:26,958 --> 00:11:28,041
In broad daylight,

162
00:11:28,125 --> 00:11:29,375
they dare to kiss right here.

163
00:11:31,500 --> 00:11:32,500
I ship them so hard!

164
00:11:36,291 --> 00:11:37,708
This is true love!

165
00:11:40,666 --> 00:11:41,666
Come on, cheers!

166
00:11:41,833 --> 00:11:43,142
To celebrate that we're still together,

167
00:11:43,166 --> 00:11:44,309
and to celebrate
overcoming all our obstacles,

168
00:11:44,333 --> 00:11:45,000
one by one.

169
00:11:45,250 --> 00:11:45,916
Cheers!

170
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:46,458
Cheers!

171
00:11:46,750 --> 00:11:49,208
To celebrate Lin Xia's
hand recovering so well!

172
00:11:49,375 --> 00:11:51,055
To celebrate Zhan Wang's health improving!

173
00:11:51,208 --> 00:11:53,000
To celebrate the great weather today!

174
00:11:53,666 --> 00:11:56,083
And to celebrate that we're
all a bit braver than yesterday!

175
00:11:56,416 --> 00:11:57,000
Cheers!

176
00:11:57,125 --> 00:11:58,125
Cheers!

177
00:12:03,875 --> 00:12:04,708
What the heck?

178
00:12:04,833 --> 00:12:06,208
Why is mine just juice?

179
00:12:06,666 --> 00:12:07,666
Mine too!

180
00:12:08,125 --> 00:12:09,916
Minors only get juice.

181
00:12:10,750 --> 00:12:11,750
No fun.

182
00:12:20,916 --> 00:12:21,916
What are you looking at?

183
00:12:22,166 --> 00:12:22,666
Eat up!

184
00:12:23,041 --> 00:12:24,041
I'm starving.

185
00:12:26,708 --> 00:12:27,750
Oh my god.

186
00:12:30,041 --> 00:12:31,041
Today,

187
00:12:32,250 --> 00:12:33,250
thank you

188
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,000
for not pushing me away.

189
00:12:36,625 --> 00:12:37,625
Push you away?

190
00:12:38,250 --> 00:12:39,250
It's just...

191
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,000
so sudden.

192
00:12:41,375 --> 00:12:42,625
I was totally caught off guard.

193
00:12:43,750 --> 00:12:44,750
But,

194
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,160
it actually felt pretty good.

195
00:12:49,541 --> 00:12:52,333
When my brother kissed Bian Ye earlier,

196
00:12:53,250 --> 00:12:54,250
someone's face

197
00:12:54,333 --> 00:12:55,708
turned as red as a tomato.

198
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,291
You weren't any better.

199
00:12:58,083 --> 00:12:59,500
Your eyes were as wide as saucers.

200
00:13:01,708 --> 00:13:02,708
It was quite shocking,

201
00:13:03,083 --> 00:13:04,083
but really satisfying.

202
00:13:04,666 --> 00:13:05,666
My brother...

203
00:13:06,250 --> 00:13:07,450
finally isn't hiding anymore.

204
00:13:13,833 --> 00:13:14,833
Then what about us?

205
00:13:18,916 --> 00:13:19,916
Boss,

206
00:13:20,291 --> 00:13:21,601
The demolition agreements
for the other shops

207
00:13:21,625 --> 00:13:22,625
have all been signed.

208
00:13:23,125 --> 00:13:24,885
Now, only the Xu Family
Noodle Shop is left.

209
00:13:25,583 --> 00:13:27,333
We've tried everything, but nothing worked.

210
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,375
The boys heard back that

211
00:13:29,666 --> 00:13:30,906
the Zhan family has stepped in.

212
00:13:31,416 --> 00:13:33,216
Are we still going ahead
with the demolition?

213
00:13:36,916 --> 00:13:37,916
Tear it down.

214
00:13:46,250 --> 00:13:47,583
Come on, another drink.

215
00:13:48,291 --> 00:13:49,958
To bravery, and to the future.

216
00:13:50,083 --> 00:13:51,000
To those messy,

217
00:13:51,001 --> 00:13:52,041
yet very special days.

218
00:13:52,791 --> 00:13:53,791
Cheers!

219
00:13:58,450 --> 00:13:59,623
[Mom]

220
00:14:01,583 --> 00:14:02,000
Mom?

221
00:14:02,375 --> 00:14:02,833
Hello.

222
00:14:03,083 --> 00:14:04,559
Are you a family member of Chen Meixi?

223
00:14:04,583 --> 00:14:05,743
This is the hospital calling.

224
00:14:06,083 --> 00:14:07,083
The hospital?

225
00:14:08,166 --> 00:14:09,750
She just fainted and was brought in.

226
00:14:09,958 --> 00:14:10,976
We need a family member to come over.

227
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,000
Which hospital?

228
00:14:12,166 --> 00:14:12,666
People's Hospital.

229
00:14:13,041 --> 00:14:13,500
Okay.

230
00:14:13,625 --> 00:14:14,666
I... I understand.

231
00:14:16,291 --> 00:14:17,451
Something happened to my mom.

232
00:14:18,291 --> 00:14:20,017
The demolition crew came to
force her to sign again today.

233
00:14:20,041 --> 00:14:21,309
They made her so angry she
fainted and was sent to the hospital.

234
00:14:21,333 --> 00:14:22,333
Mom!

235
00:14:22,875 --> 00:14:23,875
Don't panic.

236
00:14:24,083 --> 00:14:24,875
I'll go to the hospital with you.

237
00:14:25,083 --> 00:14:26,184
Where are the people
doing the forced demolition?

238
00:14:26,208 --> 00:14:27,528
At the noodle shop again?

239
00:14:27,875 --> 00:14:29,355
They said it must be torn down today.

240
00:14:29,875 --> 00:14:31,355
We can't let them get away with this.

241
00:14:31,666 --> 00:14:33,184
Lin Xia, go to the hospital with Xiao Nuo.

242
00:14:33,208 --> 00:14:33,958
Xu Yuan, let's go.

243
00:14:34,083 --> 00:14:35,083
Let's go.

244
00:14:35,916 --> 00:14:36,666
Let's go to the hospital to help.

245
00:14:36,916 --> 00:14:37,916
Let's go.

246
00:14:39,875 --> 00:14:41,835
Don't think hiding in
the hospital will save you.

247
00:14:42,166 --> 00:14:43,375
If you don't sign today,

248
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:44,791
the shop is gone.

249
00:14:47,125 --> 00:14:47,916
18 million.

250
00:14:47,958 --> 00:14:48,958
What are you doing?

251
00:14:49,833 --> 00:14:50,851
I've already called the police.

252
00:14:50,875 --> 00:14:52,435
Your demolition procedures are illegal.

253
00:14:52,833 --> 00:14:53,976
A lawyer's letter will arrive tomorrow.

254
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,000
You little punk.

255
00:14:56,125 --> 00:14:57,125
You're still wet behind the ears,

256
00:14:57,126 --> 00:14:58,846
and you're trying to lecture me on the law?

257
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:02,541
Let me tell you,

258
00:15:03,291 --> 00:15:04,291
around here,

259
00:15:04,541 --> 00:15:05,958
my word is the law.

260
00:15:08,791 --> 00:15:09,791
Get the hell out of here.

261
00:15:10,333 --> 00:15:12,253
If you don't leave, we'll
tear you down with it.

262
00:15:12,541 --> 00:15:13,541
Don't you dare!

263
00:15:16,166 --> 00:15:17,750
Doing this the hard way, huh?

264
00:15:18,708 --> 00:15:19,708
Beat them up!

265
00:15:30,291 --> 00:15:30,750
Zhan Wang!

266
00:15:31,250 --> 00:15:32,250
Run!

267
00:15:33,250 --> 00:15:34,392
Get them! Don't let them run!

268
00:15:34,416 --> 00:15:35,416
This way!

269
00:15:52,291 --> 00:15:54,011
Fortunately, it's just a flesh wound.

270
00:15:55,125 --> 00:15:56,405
No internal organs were damaged.

271
00:15:58,416 --> 00:15:59,416
It's fine.

272
00:16:00,125 --> 00:16:02,165
I used to get these kinds
of injuries all the time.

273
00:16:02,708 --> 00:16:03,708
You do it.

274
00:16:07,166 --> 00:16:08,684
Are you sure you don't
want to call Brother Xu?

275
00:16:08,708 --> 00:16:09,708
Or go to the hospital?

276
00:16:17,166 --> 00:16:18,166
I trust you.

277
00:16:34,833 --> 00:16:35,833
I'm starting then.

278
00:17:07,625 --> 00:17:08,625
Dr. Xu,

279
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:12,000
it hurts.

280
00:17:13,708 --> 00:17:15,000
Is there any other way?

281
00:17:40,333 --> 00:17:41,693
Just bear with it a little longer.

282
00:17:42,583 --> 00:17:43,583
It'll be over soon.

283
00:18:35,416 --> 00:18:36,416
You're hurt.

284
00:18:39,083 --> 00:18:40,083
Let me do it.

285
00:19:05,708 --> 00:19:06,708
Are you scared?

286
00:19:08,500 --> 00:19:09,500
No.

287
00:20:35,708 --> 00:20:36,708
You're awake.

288
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,000
Why aren't you sleeping?

289
00:20:49,875 --> 00:20:50,915
Is your wound uncomfortable?

290
00:20:53,208 --> 00:20:54,768
I was afraid that if I fell asleep,

291
00:20:55,833 --> 00:20:57,273
you wouldn't be here when I woke up.

292
00:21:00,833 --> 00:21:01,833
How could I leave?

293
00:21:03,666 --> 00:21:04,833
I'll always be by your side.

294
00:21:07,958 --> 00:21:08,958
Does your wound...

295
00:21:10,083 --> 00:21:11,083
still hurt?

296
00:21:19,250 --> 00:21:20,250
Are you hurting?

297
00:21:32,541 --> 00:21:33,541
Did you like it?

298
00:21:46,541 --> 00:21:47,541
Are you sleepy?

299
00:21:49,291 --> 00:21:50,291
No.

300
00:21:52,333 --> 00:21:53,333
I was just thinking,

301
00:21:55,750 --> 00:21:57,875
how many times have we woken up together?

302
00:22:00,625 --> 00:22:01,625
Have you counted?

303
00:22:05,666 --> 00:22:06,666
The third time.

304
00:22:08,791 --> 00:22:10,291
And this time is different.

305
00:22:34,041 --> 00:22:35,041
I'm so scared.

306
00:22:35,458 --> 00:22:37,098
I'm scared that we're dreaming right now.

307
00:22:38,208 --> 00:22:39,368
I think even if it's a dream,

308
00:22:40,541 --> 00:22:41,541
it's a

309
00:22:42,291 --> 00:22:43,291
very beautiful,

310
00:22:44,125 --> 00:22:45,125
very long,

311
00:22:46,375 --> 00:22:47,375
and very romantic dream.

312
00:22:48,708 --> 00:22:49,708
I don't want to wake up.

313
00:22:50,291 --> 00:22:51,531
I don't want to wake up either.

314
00:22:52,500 --> 00:22:53,500
Then, if

315
00:22:53,708 --> 00:22:55,668
you had to set an
expiration date for this dream,

316
00:22:56,666 --> 00:22:57,986
how long would you want it to be?

317
00:22:59,375 --> 00:23:00,375
Ten thousand years.

318
00:23:00,666 --> 00:23:01,666
Guess

319
00:23:02,083 --> 00:23:03,083
how long I want it to be.

320
00:23:04,291 --> 00:23:05,291
I can't guess.

321
00:23:06,708 --> 00:23:07,708
No expiration date.

322
00:23:08,625 --> 00:23:09,666
You're so bad.

323
00:23:16,250 --> 00:23:17,416
Bian Ye,

324
00:23:18,541 --> 00:23:21,000
we will always be together.

325
00:23:54,791 --> 00:23:55,791
Let me carry your bag.

326
00:23:56,458 --> 00:23:57,458
Sure.

327
00:23:58,041 --> 00:23:59,517
They really have a great relationship.

328
00:23:59,541 --> 00:24:00,541
They're inseparable.

329
00:24:00,708 --> 00:24:02,228
It's good that they get along so well.

330
00:24:05,250 --> 00:24:07,500
Xiao Wang even made a
special trip to bring me back.

331
00:24:07,875 --> 00:24:09,000
I heard you got hurt.

332
00:24:09,166 --> 00:24:10,000
Are you feeling better?

333
00:24:10,166 --> 00:24:11,166
I'm fine, Auntie.

334
00:24:11,333 --> 00:24:12,333
It's just a minor injury.

335
00:24:12,958 --> 00:24:14,375
I even dragged you into this.

336
00:24:15,791 --> 00:24:17,041
We're already family.

337
00:24:17,708 --> 00:24:19,548
There's no such thing
as dragging anyone down.

338
00:24:20,166 --> 00:24:21,166
It's just a pity

339
00:24:21,333 --> 00:24:22,933
the shop was still torn down in the end.

340
00:24:23,166 --> 00:24:24,526
I'm already working on a solution.

341
00:24:28,708 --> 00:24:29,083
Auntie,

342
00:24:29,541 --> 00:24:30,601
congratulations on being discharged.

343
00:24:30,625 --> 00:24:31,333
Thank you.

344
00:24:31,625 --> 00:24:32,625
You came too.

345
00:24:33,125 --> 00:24:34,845
I'll go make something for you guys to eat.

346
00:24:35,000 --> 00:24:36,375
Auntie, you just recovered.

347
00:24:36,541 --> 00:24:37,684
Please don't trouble yourself.

348
00:24:37,708 --> 00:24:38,708
It's no trouble.

349
00:24:38,750 --> 00:24:40,458
I'll help Mom inside first.

350
00:24:45,250 --> 00:24:45,916
I asked a friend

351
00:24:46,083 --> 00:24:47,892
to find a storefront at the
east entrance of the town.

352
00:24:47,916 --> 00:24:49,156
They're in a hurry to sublease.

353
00:24:49,625 --> 00:24:50,745
The location is pretty good.

354
00:24:50,875 --> 00:24:52,435
It's surrounded by long-time residents,

355
00:24:52,541 --> 00:24:53,934
so there's a good base
of regular customers.

356
00:24:53,958 --> 00:24:55,791
As for the paperwork and the initial rent,

357
00:24:56,375 --> 00:24:56,958
I can...

358
00:24:57,166 --> 00:24:58,666
It's fine, I have the money.

359
00:24:59,208 --> 00:25:00,434
Just give me the landlord's
phone number and address.

360
00:25:00,458 --> 00:25:01,458
That'll be enough.

361
00:25:02,375 --> 00:25:03,375
Alright.

362
00:25:03,416 --> 00:25:04,416
You're an adult now.

363
00:25:04,708 --> 00:25:06,916
Solving your own problems

364
00:25:07,541 --> 00:25:08,541
is a good thing.

365
00:25:08,817 --> 00:25:10,357
[Folder containing documents]

366
00:25:11,166 --> 00:25:12,166
Here.

367
00:25:13,125 --> 00:25:14,125
Take it.

368
00:25:14,375 --> 00:25:16,695
The place my second brother
found definitely won't be bad.

369
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:17,666
But

370
00:25:17,958 --> 00:25:20,198
there's one more thing I
might need to trouble you with.

371
00:25:22,083 --> 00:25:23,083
As for Lawyer Lu,

372
00:25:23,166 --> 00:25:24,226
I've already spoken with him.

373
00:25:24,250 --> 00:25:26,490
They demolished illegally
and intentionally caused harm.

374
00:25:26,875 --> 00:25:27,934
Once the lawsuit is settled,

375
00:25:27,958 --> 00:25:29,238
the compensation won't be small.

376
00:25:32,458 --> 00:25:33,458
I'm your second brother.

377
00:25:34,250 --> 00:25:36,416
How could I not know what you're thinking?

378
00:25:40,833 --> 00:25:41,833
Thank you,

379
00:25:42,541 --> 00:25:43,541
Brother.

380
00:25:48,041 --> 00:25:49,041
I'm off.

381
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:56,000
Zhan Wang,

382
00:25:56,750 --> 00:25:58,030
where did you get so much money?

383
00:25:59,375 --> 00:26:00,375
Don't worry.

384
00:26:00,458 --> 00:26:01,458
I have plenty of money.

385
00:26:02,375 --> 00:26:03,375
Zhan Wang.

386
00:26:04,125 --> 00:26:05,125
What's wrong?

387
00:26:05,166 --> 00:26:06,486
Are you worried I'll squander it?

388
00:26:06,625 --> 00:26:08,892
Then you'll have to keep a close
eye on the money from now on,

389
00:26:08,916 --> 00:26:09,916
Housekeeper Xu.

390
00:26:11,625 --> 00:26:12,625
Let's go.

391
00:26:50,583 --> 00:26:54,256
[The menu for the restaurant]

392
00:27:50,250 --> 00:27:51,250
Xiao Yuan-yuan,

393
00:27:52,250 --> 00:27:53,250
I'm here!

